text: Ilex qianlingshanensis, commonly known in China as 黔灵山冬青 (Qianling Mountain holly) is a species of plant in the family Aquifoliaceae. It is endemic to China. ==References== qianlingshanensis Category:Endemic flora of China Category:Endangered flora of Asia Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot
